          "activation_name": "Garden Sanctuary",
          "effect": "You touch the *Viridian Crown*, then pass your hand outward, palm down. A glorious and beautiful garden blossoms around you in a 30-foot emanation. The plants comprising this garden are of a type appropriate to the terrain, but if no plants are appropriate, you can choose the type. The garden\u2019s plants actively move and twist to oppose passage by your enemies, and they treat the terrain as greater difficult terrain. As long as you begin your turn in the garden sanctuary, it gains the minion trait and can use its two actions to cast spells at your direction. The garden sanctuary\u2019s spells are cast at 9th-rank, and it has 3 spell slots to cast spells each day. It can cast *field of life*, *moment of renewal*, or *tree of seasons*, treating its center as the point of origin for these spells as needed. The garden sanctuary persists until you use this activation again.",
          "frequency": "three times per day",
